  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nWhen I connect a Bluetooth keyboard to an Android phone and try to type in chat pressing `Enter` does not send a message, but instead creates a new line. This isn't what you would expect compared to any other chat application.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n* `Enter` sends the messages\r\n* `Shift+Enter` adds new line\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n* `Enter` adds new line\r\n* `Shift+Enter` adds new line\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Release `1.15.0` \r\n- Operating System: Android",
